Description: DFM right-click menu manager
 DFM Menu Manager is a graphical tool for managing the right-click
 context menu in the Deepin File Manager (DFM). It provides an easy-to-use
 interface for:
  .
  * Viewing and editing menu configuration files
  * Managing menu items and their properties
  * Configuring menu types and supported file suffixes
  * Setting menu item positions and visibility
  * Supporting both user and system-wide configurations
  .
  This tool is particularly useful for customizing the file manager's
  context menu to better suit your workflow and preferences.
